snippet.title: Adult Swim UK
snippet.description:
Fancy bumping into you here. Thanks for coming.
We’re [adult swim] uk, relatives of [adult swim] but we say tomato instead of tomato. And data instead of data.
We’re quite funny (haha and peculiar).
We like weird and freaky stuff. 
We usually last about 11 minutes, give or take, but we pack a lot in. 
 
We’re now officially in a relationship with E4 and All4. It’s complicated. 
Invite us into your world every Thursday night on E4 with some late night hilarity of the absurdist, mind-melting kind.
While on All4 it's late night, all the time. Sample our delicious video delights for free, any time you fancy.
